          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Foreclosure Fairness Act of 2015 </b></p> <p> Prohibits a court, in the case of any federally related mortgage loan made after enactment of this Act, from entering a deficiency judgment requiring the mortgagor to pay any balance on the mortgage loan after a foreclosure sale of the mortgaged property.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
